25
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:13,080
This is man-made.
I've seen a lot of this.

26
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:14,680
Since the Grand Marshal's residence
became haunted,

27
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:16,480
