28
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:18,160
It seems finding out the cause
of the Grand Marshal's death

29
00:01:18,160 --> 00:01:19,480
is the key to our return.

30
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:20,240
What do you think?

31
