and it was just an accident, do you?

64
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:19,680
That makes sense.

65
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:22,240
Let's test for drug.

66
00:02:24,640 --> 00:02:26,520
I have a beaker, a pipette,

67
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,080
